1981;;Around the World with Dot;;Australian;;Yoram Gross;;Ashley Arye, Drew Forsythe, Barbara Frawley, Ron Haddrick, Keith Scott;;animation;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Around_the_World_with_Dot;;Dot joins Santa Claus on a tour of the world to see everyone celebrate Christmas in their own different ways. They search for a long lost beloved joey.